text: Jordanoleiopus machadoi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1959.Biolib.cz - Jordanoleiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Polymistoleiopus Category:Beetles described in 1959 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
